ystal Simorgh]] for Best Director\n| ''[[In the Name of the Father (2006 film)|In the Name of the Father]]''\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[Crystal Simorgh]] for Best Screenplay\n| ''[[In the Name of the Father (2006 film)|In the Name of the Father]]''\n| {{Won|Diploma of Honor}}\n|-\n| Asian competition\n| [[Crystal Simorgh]] for Best Film{{efn|name=Pirhadi}}\n| ''[[In the Name of the Father (2006 film)|In the Name of the Father]]''\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| 2010\n| Iranian competition\n| [[Crystal Simorgh]] for Best Director\n| ''[[In Amethyst Color]]''\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| 2018\n| Iranian competition\n| [[Crystal Simorgh]] for Best Director\n| ''[[Damascus Time]]''\n| {{Won}}{{efn|Along with [[Bahram Tavakoli (Director)|Bahram Tavakoli]] for Directing of ''[[The Lost Strait]]''}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Mar del Plata International Film Festival]]\n| 2003\n| {{N/a}}\n| [[Golden Astor]] for Best Film\n| ''[[Low Heights]]''\n| {{Nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mardelplatafilmfest.com/34/en/edicion/18 |website=Mar del Plata International Film Festival |title=18th Edition (2003) |access-date=28 April 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.filmaffinity.com/en/awards.php?award_id=mar&year=2003 |website=FilmAffinity |title=18th Mar del Plata Film Festival (2003) |access-date=28 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"9\" scope=\"row\"| [[Iran Cinema Celebration]]\n| 1998\n| Feature Films\n| Golden Statuette for Best Director\n| ''[[The Glass Agency]]''\n| {{Won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"7\"| <ref name=\"Festivals\"/>\n|-\n| 1999\n| Feature Films\n| Golden Statuette for Best Director\n| ''[[The Red Ribbon]]''\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2002\n| Feature Films\n| Golden Statuette for Best Director\n| ''[[Low Heights]]''\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| Feature Films\n| Golden Statuette for Best Screenplay{{efn|Co-written with [[Asghar Farhadi]]}}\n| ''[[Low Heights]]''\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| Feature Films\n| [[Iran's Film Critics and Writers Associati